						<summary>

						<p>On a boulder in a field.</p>						

						<p>1282 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated the cyclic year Chitrabhānu, Āśvija śu. 5, Tuesday. As the record may be placed, on palaeographical grounds, in the 13th century, the details may correspond to 1282 A.D., September 8.</p>						

						<p>It records a gift of land to a Jaina temple by the <hi rend="italic">Prabhu</hi> and other residents of the place.</p>						

						</summary>
